[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":390},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201001\u002F1805633629\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201001\u002F1805633629\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201001\u002F1805633629\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201001\u002F1805633629\u002F":367,"related:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201001\u002F1805633629\u002F":376},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F01\u002Flearn-hexo-18-next-structure\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":350,"date":351,"description":18,"extension":352,"lang":353,"meta":354,"navigation":246,"path":355,"readingMinutes":356,"seo":357,"standalone":358,"stem":359,"tags":360,"tldr":364,"updated":364,"url":365,"__hash__":366},"content\u002F試著學 Hexo\u002F18-試著學-Hexo-NexT-主題篇-認識-NexT-結構.md","(18) 試著學 Hexo - NexT 主題篇 - 認識 NexT 結構","1805633629",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":341},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,63,78,81,88,95,103,105,108,110,113,115,118,126,129,151,157,161,164,167,173,176,306,309,312,327,337],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來這一篇我們就讓我們來認識一下 NexT 的結構。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"next-目錄結構","NexT 目錄結構",[24,25,26,33,38,43,48,53,58],"ul",{},[27,28,29],"li",{},[30,31,32],"code",{},"docs",[27,34,35],{},[30,36,37],{},"languages",[27,39,40],{},[30,41,42],{},"layout",[27,44,45],{},[30,46,47],{},"scripts",[27,49,50],{},[30,51,52],{},"source",[27,54,55],{},[30,56,57],{},"_config.yml",[27,59,60],{},[30,61,62],{},"gulpfile.js",[16,64,65,66,69,70,73,74,77],{},"其他沒列出來的部分是可以不用去太過在意的檔案，基本上也不太會去動到那些檔案，例如：",[30,67,68],{},".eslintrc.json","、",[30,71,72],{},".travis.yml"," 以及 ",[30,75,76],{},".editorconfig"," 等等，這些檔案都是開發一個主題時才會需要特別調整或處理的。",[16,79,80],{},"看到這邊你可能會想說：「難道用 NexT 主題還要改它的東西？！前面學那麼多難道還不夠嗎？！」",[16,82,83],{},[84,85],"img",{"alt":86,"src":87},"真沒良心！","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F2deb2e2395fa48338fb817415c3df952.jpg",[16,89,90,91,94],{},"除非你有打算做一些客製化，否則基本上你是可以不用改任何東西的，最多只會針對 ",[30,92,93],{},"themes\u002F_config.yml"," 調整。",[16,96,97,98,102],{},"但是呢... ",[99,100,101],"del",{},"為了充鐵人賽篇數"," 為了可能某些人會想要客製化模板，所以才會建議稍微認識一下它的結構。",[12,104,32],{"id":32},[16,106,107],{},"基本上 docs 資料夾顧名思義就是放一些說明文件的地方，目前主要是三個語系，分別是英語、簡體中文以及俄語。",[12,109,37],{"id":37},[16,111,112],{},"languages 資料夾底下包含了各國語言的語系包，約 22 個語系。",[12,114,42],{"id":42},[16,116,117],{},"NexT 本身模板是採用 swig 模板引擎，基本上如果你寫過 ejs 應該會格外覺得親切，因為非常相似，其中如果你是使用 VSCode 開發的話，你也可以安裝 swig 套件幫助辨識該檔案",[16,119,120],{},[121,122,123],"a",{"href":123,"rel":124},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=zhutian.swig",[125],"nofollow",[16,127,128],{},"而該資料夾底下又細分",[24,130,131,136,141,146],{},[27,132,133],{},[30,134,135],{},"_macro",[27,137,138],{},[30,139,140],{},"_partials",[27,142,143],{},[30,144,145],{},"_scripts",[27,147,148],{},[30,149,150],{},"_third-party",[16,152,153,154,156],{},"在這邊會比較需要注意的是 ",[30,155,140],{}," 資料夾，如果你想增加一些功能的話，大多都是針對該資料夾底下的 swig 修改。",[12,158,160],{"id":159},"scripts-source","scripts & source",[16,162,163],{},"這兩個資料夾基本上就是放置 CSS 與 JavaScript 的地方，當然也包含第三方插件等，其中 NexT 所採用的 CSS 預處理器是 stylus。",[16,165,166],{},"這邊你也可以安裝 language-stylus 來高亮並辨識檔案",[16,168,169],{},[121,170,171],{"href":171,"rel":172},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=sysoev.language-stylus",[125],[16,174,175],{},"如果你具有 Sass or SCSS 基礎，基本上你會看到很熟悉的樣式",[177,178,183],"pre",{"className":179,"code":180,"language":181,"meta":182,"style":182},"language-styl shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast",".header-inner {\n  background: var(--content-bg-color);\n  border-radius: $border-radius-inner;\n  box-shadow: $box-shadow-inner;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  padding: 0;\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 0;\n  width: $sidebar-desktop;\n\n  +desktop-large() {\n    width: $sidebar-desktop;\n  }\n\n  +tablet-mobile() {\n    border-radius: initial;\n    position: relative;\n    width: auto;\n  }\n}\n","styl","",[30,184,185,193,199,205,211,217,223,229,235,241,248,254,260,266,271,277,283,289,295,300],{"__ignoreMap":182},[186,187,190],"span",{"class":188,"line":189},"line",1,[186,191,192],{},".header-inner {\n",[186,194,196],{"class":188,"line":195},2,[186,197,198],{},"  background: var(--content-bg-color);\n",[186,200,202],{"class":188,"line":201},3,[186,203,204],{},"  border-radius: $border-radius-inner;\n",[186,206,208],{"class":188,"line":207},4,[186,209,210],{},"  box-shadow: $box-shadow-inner;\n",[186,212,214],{"class":188,"line":213},5,[186,215,216],{},"  overflow: hidden;\n",[186,218,220],{"class":188,"line":219},6,[186,221,222],{},"  padding: 0;\n",[186,224,226],{"class":188,"line":225},7,[186,227,228],{},"  position: absolute;\n",[186,230,232],{"class":188,"line":231},8,[186,233,234],{},"  top: 0;\n",[186,236,238],{"class":188,"line":237},9,[186,239,240],{},"  width: $sidebar-desktop;\n",[186,242,244],{"class":188,"line":243},10,[186,245,247],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":246},true,"\n",[186,249,251],{"class":188,"line":250},11,[186,252,253],{},"  +desktop-large() {\n",[186,255,257],{"class":188,"line":256},12,[186,258,259],{},"    width: $sidebar-desktop;\n",[186,261,263],{"class":188,"line":262},13,[186,264,265],{},"  }\n",[186,267,269],{"class":188,"line":268},14,[186,270,247],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":246},[186,272,274],{"class":188,"line":273},15,[186,275,276],{},"  +tablet-mobile() {\n",[186,278,280],{"class":188,"line":279},16,[186,281,282],{},"    border-radius: initial;\n",[186,284,286],{"class":188,"line":285},17,[186,287,288],{},"    position: relative;\n",[186,290,292],{"class":188,"line":291},18,[186,293,294],{},"    width: auto;\n",[186,296,298],{"class":188,"line":297},19,[186,299,265],{},[186,301,303],{"class":188,"line":302},20,[186,304,305],{},"}\n",[12,307,62],{"id":308},"gulpfilejs",[16,310,311],{},"這一支其實我從來都沒開啟來看過，因為在使用 NexT 的時候，並不會使用到該檔案，這隻檔案我快速簡單看過去主要是用於測試用，因此不用去理會它沒關係。",[16,313,314,315,318,319,322,323,326],{},"但是如果你好奇的話，你可以輸入 ",[30,316,317],{},"cd themes\u002Fnext"," 接下來安裝套件 ",[30,320,321],{},"npm install"," 並在終端機輸入 ",[30,324,325],{},"npm run test"," 就可以運作了，但是在這邊應該會噴一些錯誤，主要是第三方套件的一些錯誤，所以在此可以忽略 gulpfile.js。",[16,328,329,330,332,333,336],{},"附帶一提，如果你真的有進入到這個目錄底下輸入 ",[30,331,321],{},"，那麼請記得將 ",[30,334,335],{},"node_modules"," 刪除唷~",[338,339,340],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":182,"searchDepth":195,"depth":195,"links":342},[343,344,345,346,347,348,349],{"id":14,"depth":195,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":195,"text":22},{"id":32,"depth":195,"text":32},{"id":37,"depth":195,"text":37},{"id":42,"depth":195,"text":42},{"id":159,"depth":195,"text":160},{"id":308,"depth":195,"text":62},"Hexo","2020-10-01 00:00:10","md","zh-Hant",{},"\u002Fhexo\u002F18-hexo-next-next","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"試著學 Hexo\u002F18-試著學-Hexo-NexT-主題篇-認識-NexT-結構",[350,361,362,363],"試著學 Hexo","第 12 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽","NexT",null,"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201001\u002F1805633629\u002F","yqk8MsWKqJI12MJKVyoquTsNwVdV5SOwshJjdV-H8xs",{"newer":368,"older":372},{"url":369,"title":370,"date":371},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201002\u002F1128269164\u002F","(19) 試著學 Hexo - NexT 主題篇 - 第三方服務","2020-10-02 00:00:01",{"url":373,"title":374,"date":375},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200930\u002F1081826307\u002F","(17) 試著學 Hexo - NexT 主題篇 - NexT","2020-09-30 00:00:01",[377,381,386],{"url":378,"title":379,"date":380,"readingMinutes":356},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20221030\u002F561405053\u002F","解決 Hexo 更新系統或使用 CI 部署後文章出現更新日期的問題","2022-10-30 11:52:35",{"url":382,"title":383,"date":384,"readingMinutes":385},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201101\u002F60919\u002F","(33)試著學 Hexo-番外篇之更新 NexT 主題","2020-11-01 13:21:00","3",{"url":387,"title":388,"date":389,"re